{"type": "article", "id": 49203, "title": "阿里巴巴再次登上美国“恶名市场”名单，以及，来看看米兰时装周 | 浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的新闻。", "date": "2018-01-15T04:15:49Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 41071, "name": "Alexa Chung"}, {"id": 779, "name": "Prada"}, {"id": 7397, "name": "MSGM"}, {"id": 1231, "name": "PUMA"}, {"id": 354, "name": "阿里巴巴"}, {"id": 3134, "name": "Versace"}, {"id": 1060, "name": "H&M"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 699895, "comment_count": 9, "praise_count": 22, "image": "img/article/article_show/20180115113403RKhSwZ4dGkgoOHBm.jpg", "contents": "<h3 finallycleanhtml=\"true\">一些重要的新闻：</h3><p><a href=\"http://uk.fashionnetwork.com/news/H-M-stores-trashed-in-South-Africa-over-ad-protests,935840.html#.WlwRuVT1UzU\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>H&amp;M 在南非的门店遭打砸抗议</strong></a> | 因为涉嫌种族歧视的“丛林中最酷的猴子”广告事件持续发酵，H&amp;M 在南非约翰内斯堡的六家店铺遭到了南非经济自由斗士（EFF）组织的打砸，人体模特被推倒，店内衣物及设施被捣毁。目前，南非警方已将约翰内斯堡 H&amp;M 商店涉嫌种族歧视的广告清除。H&amp;M 随即在当地时间周六公告南非的 17 家分店将暂时关闭，确认安全后会重新开业。</p><p><a href=\"http://uk.fashionnetwork.com/news/Italy-s-Versace-in-no-rush-to-list-on-stock-market-CEO,935899.html#.WlwQGFT1UzU\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>Versace 的 CEO 说，不急着上市</strong></a> | 周六，Versace 的 CEO Jonathan Akeroyd 在接受路透社采访时说，在 2018 秋冬系列之前“还有很多工作要做”，公司并不急着上市。这项说法间接否定了路透社之前传出的 Versace 计划紧随 Valentino 上市的传闻，但并未给出更多的细节。</p><p><a href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2018-01-12/alibaba-criticized-again-by-u-s-for-selling-fakes-online\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>阿里巴巴再次登上美国贸易代表办公室的“恶名市场”</strong></a> | 上周五，阿里巴巴再次被美国贸易代表办公室列入“恶名市场”，该机构认为，执法程序的繁重和不足，导致阿里巴巴仍无法阻止平台上出售假冒产品。阿里巴巴的总裁 Michael Evans 回应称，“这不是阿里巴巴在保护版权方面的准确体现，我们别无选择，只能断定这是一个严重的、有偏见的、政治化的过程”。</p><h3>一些值得一看的：</h3><p>钟小姐<a href=\"http://www.vogue.co.uk/gallery/alexa-chung-label-third-season-collection\" rel=\"nofollow\"> Alexa Chung </a>个人同名品牌的第三个系列 Fantasic，以经典乐队的照片做灵感，融合了 90 年代英国流行音乐文化。你觉得好看吗？ </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180115112142BgnZaqCNey2xw9QG.jpeg\" data-ratio=\"1.437037\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180115112141Ffl8BItWA1mdx56V.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201801151121417gIExXUAZGKl9keY.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/2018011511214267LS48dGYoeljsmF.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180115112142HvxNnMO2qzFmpaDR.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180115112142toGkc3KaypvhDHde.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180115112143ihc67q1FWb5Lk8PK.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180115112143TkYtDx9hn7FdKBJi.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180115112144PSEoqCz6LMFftkwh.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180115112144mauBlbyKj6XsYQNZ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201801151121457ciUHm5VEO4eFYxD.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180115112145JYoWjD1LqkS7KXFV.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201801151121464kju1SNXYa7veMpO.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201801151121464tkYrpyRbUIJaEwQ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201801151121464abO6r5yGJWkuxRw.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180115112147J65yEd7RvWGAzCjf.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180115112147jNulW940GgOP5aLw.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180115112147PQGK7FDjXmYkg3wp.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180115112148fCJQnrpscxwhPo02.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201801151121487jiVg6vwY5xsa82H.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180115112149bLSnVxUC1zvjhG9P.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180115112149PwZWuzrNgDAf5SXy.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180115112149GP5VMKjUJxW6XBZp.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180115112149LuG9cQTWXeyt7gNC.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>Cara Delevingne 为 PUMA 拍摄最新广告片<a href=\"https://hypebae.com/2018/1/cara-delevingne-puma-muse-x-strap-peach\" rel=\"nofollow\">“DO YOU”</a>，发布全新的粉色缎面鞋 Muse X Strap。</p><p>这双鞋将于 1 月 18 日正式上架。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180115112111s2rHe4IuOhjTZ6Cp.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180115112110Iy7s4Vf9g0J5NQmU.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180115112111Z3AwGRm4WCsgvKfe.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180115112109H4yBd3J1CMZ9fD2W.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.665833\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180115112109GrLmqhtfHUibOwDW.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.665833\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180115112110Za2jnGPKSExvqyHw.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.665833\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><a href=\"https://www.highsnobiety.com/p/gosha-rubchinskiy-fw18-adidas-burberry/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Gosha Rubchinskiy 继续他的本土时装秀。</a>这次，Gosha 的秀场搬到了叶卡捷琳堡，展示了品牌与另外四大品牌的合作系列——Levi’s、Burberry、adidas 以及最新加入的 Doc Martens。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180115112005OPNphcIwSQkrAxdl.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.451104\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180115112005fevU1PbAxr8R7s9H.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.451104\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180115112005L7oOVn36ZWgUbEyi.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.451104\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201801151120578nCHUGQ3Zl0cAzKe.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.451104\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>米兰时装周上，各大品牌纷纷发布 2018 秋冬新品。</p><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/runway/mens-fall-collections-2018/milan/prada/review/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Prada </a>回到了 90 年代，重新在十多年前品牌面料黑色尼龙上做文章。大秀之前，Muiccia Prada 说，想回到“实用的、理性的、工业的灵魂”。在新的系列里，用了优雅的方式重新诠释作为工业标杆的尼龙。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201801151122305LGWMFyBox4cki1U.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180115112231Fkd5G1YnQwWZgKmp.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.502196\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><f